{"tid":303304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國北方遭遇有記錄以來最嚴重旱災","createTime":"2017-06-30T05:32:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T17:49:28.000Z","uid":22675,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dabd96cd43a53b5d4172ebbe3ee41542a057d7e9","tid":303304,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:32:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20170630/china-drought/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fchina%2F20170630%2Fchina-drought%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=EfBRsQ8Y9NwBYfX3EX3kCV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=02a22dec\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/china/20170630/china-drought/zh-hant/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2016/10/27/world/27CHINASTERNBERG-web1/27CHINASTERNBERG-web1-articleLarge.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01.nyt.com%2Fimages%2F2016%2F10%2F27%2Fworld%2F27CHINASTERNBERG-web1%2F27CHINASTERNBERG-web1-articleLarge.jpg&h=35b57408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年6月30日<br />\n<br />\n管理著中國北方大片區域的官員說，那裡正遭受著有記錄以來最嚴重的旱災，農作物枯萎，農牧民為農田、草原、動物和家人找水發愁。<br />\n<br />\n這場乾旱正在影響距離北京不遠的內蒙古自治區的東北部和東部地區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n習近平等中國領導人說，氣候變化是各國必須共同解決的緊迫問題，他們堅定主張各國要遵守巴黎氣候協定，雖然川普本月宣布美國將退出這個協定。<br />\n<br />\n美國在歷史上是世界最大的溫室氣體排放國，而目前最大的排放國是中國。<br />\n<br />\n在內蒙古面積巨大的呼倫貝爾市，官方統計數據顯示，近期的乾旱已經造成了53億元人民幣的經濟損失。<br />\n<br />\n該市是一個鄉村地區，有草原和牧民，毗鄰俄羅斯，曾經被稱為滿洲的地區就在它的東邊。<br />\n<br />\n呼倫貝爾的官員說，全市草場受旱面積9876萬畝。<br />\n<br />\n他們表示，地方政府投入抗旱資金1.09億元，投入抗旱人員13.3萬人。<br />\n<br />\n另一個大城市通遼的旱情也很嚴重。官方通訊社新華社的照片顯示了乾旱土地上的農作物，以及農民澆灌農田的場面。<br />\n<br />\n從空中看，大片土地呈現棕色，毫無生機。<br />\n<br />\n國家新聞媒體上個月開始報導這場旱災，稱自從4月中旬以來，由於缺少降水，旱情正在惡化。<br />\n<br />\n新華社說，截至5月下旬，有12萬人、50萬頭大牲畜因旱飲水困難。<br />\n<br />\n該報導引用了水利部部長陳雷的說法。<br />\n<br />\n陳雷說，已經有550萬人加入了抗旱行動。他們試圖通過打井或建泵站進行抗旱澆地。<br />\n<br />\n5月份，華北大部分地區經歷了極端高溫。<br />\n<br />\n雖然月底出現短暫降雨，帶來了緩解旱情的希望，但是高溫和乾旱並未消退。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府一直在大力遏制或扭轉中國北方地區沙漠的擴張，特別是在內蒙古。<br />\n<br />\n多年來，中國的沙漠以每年1300多平方英里（約合3367平方公里）的速度擴張，戈壁向南邊的北京推進。<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，植樹的努力產生了成效，儘管有些科學家認為，這個策略對阻止沙漠擴張沒有什麼效果。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府也試圖限制牧民的流動，說他們的牲畜正在把草原變成沙漠。有學者說，這個政策是錯誤的，放牧並不是荒漠化的主要原因。"},{"pid":"dff508d7e5299d25258688ea2164cf1d46f90678","tid":303304,"uid":2772,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:42:58.000Z","msg":"彭麗媛落撚左黎<br />\n上面就乾塘<br />\n<br />\n係咪暗示習種狗夫人多水"},{"pid":"964d950f5d973ba09acc53764c7d63e8772541b3","tid":303304,"uid":32906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:46:44.000Z","msg":"無呆時候民變"},{"pid":"435889d89d455b3f1de4c7424176ecfb28b14dd6","tid":303304,"uid":32906,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無咪時候民變</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c96c8729e50b8f635742cd37a469fd6530842152","tid":303304,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:51:39.000Z","msg":"支那咁強大咁有錢<br />\n成個支那變沙漠都未驚"},{"pid":"cd3a460d8e055aecc0cc27756227b2b59dbda6a2","tid":303304,"uid":39846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T05:53:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無咪時候民變</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜仲未係&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n依家全球化之下要有餓得死人嘅飢荒起碼要乾五年以上。<br />\n當然如果人仔爆破就另一個講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00299eeda3db12f686e617e60fe9a1dc9c9ced5","tid":303304,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592f9c207e0acade47f5081b5cb45594103ad1a0","tid":303304,"uid":8577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"多難興邦呀香港人<br />\n識乜𨶙呀你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"331aa0d2437692c6c8e2f498bbce1a3f47ae387f","tid":303304,"uid":94484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:19:45.000Z","msg":"又出現百年一遇喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7132e09c4f907673dd6e1f92827ff5100924b84a","tid":303304,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"de2da49ff74085d36ead3f49a48f0ce16763ea56","tid":303304,"uid":531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:30:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">美國在歷史上是世界最大的溫室氣體排放國，而目前最大的排放國是中國。</span><br />\n<br />\n咁中國抵死喎"},{"pid":"a743bdc21a7ae80bd2eaafe928a02e07f5b90ea6","tid":303304,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T08:33:33.000Z","msg":"中國人既開發方法五千年來透支晒啦，邊有得搞"},{"pid":"8ff80d07ff219427d2a2a4da850d5d603094c44b","tid":303304,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa72bef4abc4cd4d513ddb18a3a8a74a82b3578","tid":303304,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T14:57:17.000Z","msg":"中國旱災好似已經成千幾2000年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f3141dea049e632f1807461fc74fb275071704","tid":303304,"uid":53705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:02:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無咪時候民變</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可惜仲未係&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n依家全球化之下要有餓得死人嘅飢荒起碼要乾五年以上。<br />\n當然如果人仔爆破就另一個講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大躍進都餓死左3000萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1bae936e4dd59c43564ee7250582344f461f39","tid":303304,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T15:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國旱災好似已經成千幾2000年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中國幾乎每年都有天災<br />\n<br />\n睇中史書<br />\n來來去去情節都係 <br />\n乜乜地區發生 水災/地震/旱災 &gt; 官員 侵蝕物資 &gt; 災民暴動,起義 &gt; 官兵鎮壓屠殺<br />\n無限LOOP<br />\n<br />\n不過自從中共執政<br />\n情節就變左<br />\n乜乜地區發生 水災/地震/旱災 &gt; 救援人員 辛苦地救出災民 &gt; 總理李克強到當地發表講話, 親自指揮救援 &gt; 死亡人數35人"},{"pid":"b38613d6224ce0a27f0022f9ec1f57ac94bc6864","tid":303304,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:10:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67656560a3b6e014945b6e2c42b735356b419518","tid":303304,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:11:21.000Z","msg":"與天鬥,其樂無窮"},{"pid":"68b1d88c2ca32d5353e2762fd1fe1fc36b78022d","tid":303304,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2980a9def860fc8fa428d9e45fa17262a63d081c","tid":303304,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"558cb3d40ff337d1a7eec6133b6778c4958e723c","tid":303304,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T17:49:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}